"{\"value\":{\"mdx\":\"# The Outpost\\n\\n## Ranks & Rewards\\n\\nClaim up to **45% cashback** on every trade.\\n\\nHead over to [Interstate.so](https://interstate.so) and complete the required steps to start earning your cashback right away.\\n\\n---\\n\\n## Rewards\\n\\n### Gold\\n\\nGold is the foundation of the Outpost reward system. You accumulate Gold with every action you take on the platform — every trade executed and every quest completed adds to your balance.\\n\\n- **Trade to earn** — Receive Gold for every dollar in volume you generate.\\n- **Daily streaks** — Keep your trading streak alive for daily Gold bonuses. The longer your streak, the larger the reward.\\n- **Rank progression** — Climbing through the ranks earns you Gold payouts and unlocks higher Gold multipliers.\\n- **Quests** — Complete daily and seasonal quests to collect additional Gold.\\n- **Special events** — Watch for limited-time quests that award bonus Gold and multiplier boosts.\\n\\n### Solana\\n\\nSolana rewards come from two sources: Cashback and the Referral System. As you advance through the Outpost ranks and engage with quests, your cashback can reach up to **45%**, and your referral fee share can climb as high as **50%**.\\n\\n---\\n\\n## Outpost Ranks\\n\\nThe Outpost is built around progression. Each rank you reach unlocks larger multipliers, better rewards, and exclusive perks.\\n\\n| Rank | Cashback | Gold Multiplier |\\n| --- | --- | --- |\\n| **Degen** | 10% | 1x |\\n| **Warrior** | 15% | 2x |\\n| **Gladiator** | 20% | 2.5x |\\n| **Commander** | 25% | 3x |\\n| **Titan** | 35% | 4x |\\n\",\"document\":[{\"href\":\"/rewards#the-outpost\",\"html\":\"</header>\\n\",\"id\":\"docs/pages/rewards.mdx#the-outpost\",\"isPage\":true,\"text\":\"\\n\",\"title\":\"The Outpost\",\"titles\":[]},{\"href\":\"/rewards#ranks--rewards\",\"html\":\"\\n<p>Claim up to <strong>45% cashback</strong> on every trade.</p>\\n<p>Head over to <a href=\\\"https://interstate.so\\\">Interstate.so</a> and complete the required steps to start earning your cashback right away.</p>\\n<hr/>\\n\",\"id\":\"docs/pages/rewards.mdx#ranks--rewards\",\"isPage\":false,\"text\":\"\\nClaim up to 45% cashback on every trade.\\nHead over to Interstate.so and complete the required steps to start earning your cashback right away.\\n\\n\",\"title\":\"Ranks &amp; Rewards\",\"titles\":[\"The Outpost\"]},{\"href\":\"/rewards#rewards\",\"html\":\"\\n\",\"id\":\"docs/pages/rewards.mdx#rewards\",\"isPage\":false,\"text\":\"\\n\",\"title\":\"Rewards\",\"titles\":[\"The Outpost\"]},{\"href\":\"/rewards#gold\",\"html\":\"\\n<p>Gold is the foundation of the Outpost reward system. You accumulate Gold with every action you take on the platform — every trade executed and every quest completed adds to your balance.</p>\\n<ul>\\n<li><strong>Trade to earn</strong> — Receive Gold for every dollar in volume you generate.</li>\\n<li><strong>Daily streaks</strong> — Keep your trading streak alive for daily Gold bonuses. The longer your streak, the larger the reward.</li>\\n<li><strong>Rank progression</strong> — Climbing through the ranks earns you Gold payouts and unlocks higher Gold multipliers.</li>\\n<li><strong>Quests</strong> — Complete daily and seasonal quests to collect additional Gold.</li>\\n<li><strong>Special events</strong> — Watch for limited-time quests that award bonus Gold and multiplier boosts.</li>\\n</ul>\\n\",\"id\":\"docs/pages/rewards.mdx#gold\",\"isPage\":false,\"text\":\"\\nGold is the foundation of the Outpost reward system. You accumulate Gold with every action you take on the platform — every trade executed and every quest completed adds to your balance.\\n\\nTrade to earn — Receive Gold for every dollar in volume you generate.\\nDaily streaks — Keep your trading streak alive for daily Gold bonuses. The longer your streak, the larger the reward.\\nRank progression — Climbing through the ranks earns you Gold payouts and unlocks higher Gold multipliers.\\nQuests — Complete daily and seasonal quests to collect additional Gold.\\nSpecial events — Watch for limited-time quests that award bonus Gold and multiplier boosts.\\n\\n\",\"title\":\"Gold\",\"titles\":[\"The Outpost\",\"Rewards\"]},{\"href\":\"/rewards#solana\",\"html\":\"\\n<p>Solana rewards come from two sources: Cashback and the Referral System. As you advance through the Outpost ranks and engage with quests, your cashback can reach up to <strong>45%</strong>, and your referral fee share can climb as high as <strong>50%</strong>.</p>\\n<hr/>\\n\",\"id\":\"docs/pages/rewards.mdx#solana\",\"isPage\":false,\"text\":\"\\nSolana rewards come from two sources: Cashback and the Referral System. As you advance through the Outpost ranks and engage with quests, your cashback can reach up to 45%, and your referral fee share can climb as high as 50%.\\n\\n\",\"title\":\"Solana\",\"titles\":[\"The Outpost\",\"Rewards\"]},{\"href\":\"/rewards#outpost-ranks\",\"html\":\"\\n<p>The Outpost is built around progression. Each rank you reach unlocks larger multipliers, better rewards, and exclusive perks.</p>\\n<table><thead><tr><th>Rank</th><th>Cashback</th><th>Gold Multiplier</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><strong>Degen</strong></td><td>10%</td><td>1x</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Warrior</strong></td><td>15%</td><td>2x</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Gladiator</strong></td><td>20%</td><td>2.5x</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Commander</strong></td><td>25%</td><td>3x</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Titan</strong></td><td>35%</td><td>4x</td></tr></tbody></table>\",\"id\":\"docs/pages/rewards.mdx#outpost-ranks\",\"isPage\":false,\"text\":\"\\nThe Outpost is built around progression. Each rank you reach unlocks larger multipliers, better rewards, and exclusive perks.\\nRankCashbackGold MultiplierDegen10%1xWarrior15%2xGladiator20%2.5xCommander25%3xTitan35%4x\",\"title\":\"Outpost Ranks\",\"titles\":[\"The Outpost\"]}]}}"
